            "description": "Analyzes a customer support ticket to extract sentiment, priority level, and generate a summary.\n\n**Request Body:** Plain text string containing the customer message\n\n**Response:** AnalysisResult object containing:\n- sentiment: (ANGRY, NEUTRAL, HAPPY, FRUSTRATED)\n- priority: (URGENT, MEDIUM, LOW)\n- summary: AI-generated summary of the ticket"
          },
          "response": []
        },
